name: Send TT Yet to Withdraw
query:
SELECT
`tabSend TT`.`name` as "MTCN",
	CASE `tabSend TT`.docstatus
		when 0 then "Not Submitted"
		when 1 then "Submitted"
		else		"Cancel"
	END as "Status:150",
`tabSend TT`.posting_date as "Posting Date",
`tabSend TT`.sender_from_location as "From City",
`tabSend TT`.sender_from_country as "From Country",
`tabSend TT`.receiver_to as "To Country",
`tabSend TT`.receiver_to_location as "To City",
`tabSend TT`.sender_currency as "Send Currency",
`tabSend TT`.received_currency as "Received Currency",
`tabSend TT`.amount_send as "Amount Send",
`tabSend TT`.exchange_rate as "Exchange Rate",
`tabSend TT`.amount_received as "Amount Received",
`tabSend TT`.sender_name as "Sender Name",
`tabSend TT`.receiver_name as "Receiver Name",
`tabSend TT`.send_date as "Send Date",
`tabUser`.full_name as "Send By",
`tabSend TT`.withdraw_status as "Withdraw Status"
FROM
`tabSend TT`, `tabAgents`, `tabUser`
WHERE
`tabSend TT`.send_by = `tabAgents`.agent_user
AND
`tabAgents`.agent_user = `tabUser`.email
